ed="T" n="0880a20"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0880a20"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000014782">天台山福<ptr target="#n724"/>田寺</placeName><persName key="A012847">普岸</persName>傳（<persName key="A013732">全亮</persName> <persName key="A013734">唯約</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0880a21"/><persName key="A012847">釋普岸</persName>，姓<name>蔡</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000028309">漢東</placeName>人也<ptr target="#n725"/>。沖弱<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2181"/>之齡，逈然聰<lb
ed="T" n="0880a22"/>敏，骨目奇秀，天生不嗜葷羶，長有出塵之<lb
ed="T" n="0880a23"/>意。其父嚴毅<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2182"/>，訓授經籍，漸通其義，秉翰伸<lb
ed="T" n="0880a24"/>辭，宛然華<anchor xml:id="beg0880sgsz1"/>藻<anchor xml:id="end0880sgsz1"/>。因入僧舍，暫執經卷，乃歎曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0880a25"/>「佛法玄微<ptr type="glossary" target="#g773"/>，非造次<ptr type="glossary" target="#g619"/>可及！」決志辭親。時<persName key="A001897">懷海<lb
ed="T" n="0880a26"/><roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>居<placeName key="PL000000019628">百丈山</placeName>，毳<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1417"/>納之人駢肩累足，時號<lb
ed="T" n="0880a27"/>「大<anchor xml:id="beg0880003"/>叢<anchor xml:id="end0880003"/>林」焉。<persName key="A012847">岸</persName>叩其關，<persName key="A001897">海</persName>攝受<ref type="person" target="#A012847">之</ref>。日隨普請<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2183"/><lb
ed="T" n="0880a28"/>施役，夜獨執燭誦經，曾不憚勞，遂諧剃<lb
ed="T" n="0880a29"/>染。及陞戒品，便習禪那<ptr type="glossary" target="#g227"/>，壁坐忘疲，觀心恒<pb ed="T" n="0880b" xml:id="T50.2061.0880b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0880b01"/>務。<anchor xml:id="beg0880sgsz3"/>瞻蔔<anchor xml:id="end0880sgsz3"/><ptr type="glossary" target="#g525"/>附風而香遠，虥<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2180"/>貓逢獸而吼高，學<lb
ed="T" n="0880b02"/>者成圍，請於<placeName key="PL000000027662"><placeName>安陸</placeName><placeName>壽山院</placeName></placeName>坐道場矣。如是<lb
ed="T" n="0880b03"/>環拱可四百餘眾，執器聽<persName key="A001878">瞿沙</persName>之說<ptr target="#n621"/>，投籌<lb
ed="T" n="0880b04"/>待<persName key="A002397"><anchor xml:id="beg0880sgsz4"/>毱多<anchor xml:id="end0880sgsz4"/></persName>之度<ptr target="#n3359"/>。大利群機<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2184"/>，得道者眾。<date notBefore-iso="+0827-03-18" key="j20231922026427" notAfter-iso="+0836-01-25"><name>大和</name>年<lb
ed="T" n="0880b05"/>中</date>，謂眾曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A012847">吾</ref>山水之遊未厭，諸人勿相留<lb
ed="T" n="0880b06"/>滯。<placeName key="PL000000014519"><placeName>天台</placeName><placeName>赤城</placeName></placeName>，<persName key="A002299">道猷</persName>曾止息焉<ptr target="#n3360"/>；<placeName key="PL000000014426"><placeName>華頂</placeName><placeName>石梁</placeName></placeName>，<persName key="A001301">智者</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0880b07"/>昔降魔矣<ptr target="#n3361"/>！將遊之也。」自<placeName key="PL000000027118">襄陽</placeName>邐迤而來，<lb
ed="T" n="0880b08"/>從<placeName key="PL000000013444">沃洲</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000013336">天姥</placeName>入<placeName key="PL000000014411">天台</placeName>之西門得平川<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2185"/>，谷中<lb
ed="T" n="0880b09"/>峯名<placeName key="PL000000014617">大舍</placeName><ptr target="#n3363"/>，號「平田」是也<ptr target="#n3362"/>。觀<ref type="place" target="#PL000000014617">其山</ref>四舍<ptr target="#n3365"/>欝<lb
ed="T" n="0880b10"/>翠，東西山<placeName key="PL000000014440">石門</placeName><ptr target="#n3366"/>而有<placeName key="PL000000014442">三井龍潭</placeName>。東入<placeName key="PL000000014717">石橋<lb
ed="T" n="0880b11"/>聖寺</placeName>，乃是綠身<persName key="A002299">道猷<roleName>尊者</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n3364"/>結茅居此。未幾，<lb
ed="T" n="0880b12"/>見虓虎乳子，瞪目而視<persName key="A012847">岸</persName>。<persName key="A012847">岸</persName>以杖<anchor xml:id="beg0880sgsz5"/>按<anchor xml:id="end0880sgsz5"/>其頭<lb
ed="T" n="0880b13"/>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A012847">貧道</ref>聞<ref type="place" target="#PL000000014617">此山</ref>是神仙窟宅，羅漢隱居，今欲<lb
ed="T" n="0880b14"/>寄此安禪，檀越勿相驚撓。」經宿，領子而去。<lb
ed="T" n="0880b15"/>以<date key="j20256562025656" when-iso="+0833-12-15"><name>大和</name>七年癸丑十月二十七日</date>營構丈室，<lb
ed="T" n="0880b16"/>携一童侍，給薪水耳。<date from-iso="+0834-02-17" key="j20257202025808" to-iso="+0834-05-16">八年春</date>，禪侶輻湊，眾<lb
ed="T" n="0880b17"/>力義成此院，號<placeName key="PL000000014782">平田</placeName>焉。<date notBefore-iso="+0836-01-26" key="j20264282028267" notAfter-iso="+0841-02-07"><name>開成</name>中</date>，宛是大道<lb
ed="T" n="0880b18"/>場。<date from-iso="+0843-08-04" key="j20291752029203" to-iso="+0843-09-01"><name>會昌</name>三年七月</date>，告眾入滅，春秋七十四。<lb
ed="T" n="0880b19"/>度弟子<persName key="A013732">全亮</persName>，俗姓<name>陳</name>氏，悟<ref type="person" target="#A012847">師</ref>之道，得鳳之<lb
ed="T" n="0880b20"/>毛<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2186"/>，一人！<persName key="A013734">唯約</persName>，在<placeName key="PL000000008820">上元</placeName>入滅，肉身不朽。<persName key="A012847">岸</persName>遷<lb
ed="T" n="0880b21"/>塔于是山前，此寺置五百羅漢殿，<placeName key="PL000000012522">永嘉</placeName><persName key="A013733">全億</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0880b22"/>長史<anchor xml:id="beg0880sgsz7"/>畫<anchor xml:id="end0880sgsz7"/>半千形像，每一迎請，必於<placeName key="PL000000014717">石橋</placeName>宿<lb
ed="T" n="0880b23"/>夜焚香，具幢蓋、螺鈸，引導入于殿，香風送<lb
ed="T" n="0880b24"/>至。幡幢之勢前靡，而入門即止。其<placeName key="PL000000014717">石梁聖寺</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0880b25"/>在<placeName key="PL000000014426">石橋</placeName>之裏。梵唄方作，香靄始飄。先有金色<lb
ed="T" n="0880b26"/>鳥飛翔，後林樹石畔見<name>梵</name>僧，或行或坐，或<lb
ed="T" n="0880b27"/>招手之狀，或臥空之形，眴息之間，千變萬化。<lb
ed="T" n="0880b28"/><placeName key="PL000000008355">漢南</placeName>國王<name>錢</name>氏頻年施供養，祥瑞極繁。<ref type="person" target="#A001640">今上</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0880b29"/><date from-iso="+0978-02-15" key="j20783132078667" to-iso="+0979-02-04"><name>太平興國</name>三年</date>，於<placeName key="PL000000023404">滋福殿</placeName>宣問<ptr type="glossary" target="#g779"/><placeName key="PL000000011455">兩浙</placeName>都僧正<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2187"/><pb ed="T" n="0880c" xml:id="T50.2061.0880c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0880c01"/><persName key="A001910">贊寧</persName><placeName key="PL000000014426">石橋</placeName>長廣量度，一皆實<anchor xml:id="beg0880004"/>奏<anchor xml:id="end0880004"/>，<ref type="person" target="#A001640">帝</ref>歎嗟久<lb
ed="T" n="0880c02"/>之。至<date from-iso="+0983-02-21" key="j20801452080498" to-iso="+0984-02-09">八年</date>因<placeName key="PL000000014782">福田寺</placeName>道者<persName key="A015197">自詢</persName>誓斷腕然<lb
ed="T" n="0880c03"/>鍊，乞重造<ref type="place" target="#PL000000014782">此寺</ref>，乃宣內殿頭高品<persName key="A010043">衛紹欽</persName>、<persName key="A013735">張<lb
ed="T" n="0880c04"/>承貴</persName>革故規制，若化出天宮焉。今<persName key="A012847">岸<roleName>師</roleName></persName>影<lb
ed="T" n="0880c05"/>堂在<ref type="place" target="#PL000000014782">寺</ref>之右。</p>
